       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ARRAYS-BASICOS-RPG.
      * Programa que demuestra la manipulación de arrays
      * Utiliza GitHub Copilot para sugerir operaciones de array
      
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-ARRAY-NUMEROS.
           05  WS-NUMERO PIC 9(3) OCCURS 10 TIMES.
       
       01  WS-ARRAY-NOMBRES.
           05  WS-NOMBRE PIC X(30) OCCURS 5 TIMES.
       
       01  WS-INDICE PIC 9(2).
       01  WS-SUMA PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.
       01  WS-PROMEDIO PIC 9(4)V99.
       
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      * Llenar el array de números
           PERFORM VARYING WS-INDICE FROM 1 BY 1
               UNTIL WS-INDICE > 10
               MOVE FUNCTION RANDOM * 100 TO WS-NUMERO(WS-INDICE)
           END-PERFORM.
           
      * Calcular suma y promedio
           PERFORM VARYING WS-INDICE FROM 1 BY 1
               UNTIL WS-INDICE > 10
               ADD WS-NUMERO(WS-INDICE) TO WS-SUMA
           END-PERFORM.
           
           DIVIDE WS-SUMA BY 10 GIVING WS-PROMEDIO.
           
           DISPLAY 'Array de números:'.
           PERFORM VARYING WS-INDICE FROM 1 BY 1
               UNTIL WS-INDICE > 10
               DISPLAY 'Elemento ' WS-INDICE ': ' 
                   WS-NUMERO(WS-INDICE)
           END-PERFORM.
           
           DISPLAY 'Suma total: ' WS-SUMA.
           DISPLAY 'Promedio: ' WS-PROMEDIO.
           STOP RUN.